{
  "stem": "8842.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the general direction was the closest possible to the near-- as close as the-- the border, it was It wasn't really important, probably, which city we're going to hit, or at least to escape to go over the border to be under the Russian regime.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At this point, I don't think it was important to our parents where they're going to take us at this point.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as far as I could remember is we-- we went about 80 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how to exchange that in miles, but it wasn't very far when--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "80 80.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "8-0.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About 80 kilometers through the roads, little villages, stopping here, stopping there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, because of the airplanes that were all over us, fast, nobody could go with so much old and young kids.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- it was a very-- a terrible ordeal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is as far as we could make it when the-- we-- somebody came ahead of us telling us there's no use to go any further because the Germans already ahead of us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they are pushing us back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're going to come and they will push us back, going back to Kovno.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's nowhere to escape anymore because the border-- the Russian border-- was already-- was still too far from us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we turned around, and we start heading back home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her feet were a disaster.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were so swollen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were so with boils, and-- and probably the-- positively the wrong shoes-wearing and everything else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So every time somebody else could catch and put her on something, or my father on the bicycle, kept her moving on as much as possible to help her out.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We reached Kovno again, not direct to our house because our home was in a very different direction.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
